'''''Olympia''''', ni Ikinamico y'urukundo muri Amerika yo muri 2018 iyobowe na Gregory Dixon nk'umukinnyi  wambere kandi afatanije na McKenzie Chinn, Gregory Dixon, Lucy Lola Manda na Elliott Lonsdale kumashusho 30, Isosiyete ikora umurongo wa firime<ref>http://reelhonestreviews.com/6563-2/</ref><ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/olympia_2018</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo McKenzie Chinn mu mwanya wâ€™icyubahiro mu gihe Charles Andrew Gardner, Ericka Ratcliff, LaNisa Renee Frederick na Penelope Walker bagize uruhare runini.<ref>https://www.dixonimage.com/profile</ref> 

Filime yakiriwe neza  kandi yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://beloitfilmfest.org/films/olympia/</ref>.   Yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 22 Nzeri 2018 mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Los Angeles. Hanyuma yerekanwe ku ya 15 Ukwakira 2018 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Chicago ku ya 5 Mata 2019 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya RiverRun <ref>https://riverrunfilm.com/film/olympia-narrative</ref>.<ref>https://www.yesweekly.com/film/riverrun-announces-2019-film-lineup-ode-to-joy-this-changes-everything-to-open-spotlight-on/article_c4b31e19-bcce-587b-a909-13223fa44332.html</ref>  

